   <concept id="FAR_15_607" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">15.607</ph> Criteria for acceptance and negotiation of an unsolicited proposal.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d946e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            A favorable comprehensive evaluation of an unsolicited proposal does not, in itself, justify awarding a contract without providing for full and open competition. The agency point of contact shall return an unsolicited proposal to the offeror, citing reasons, when its substance-</p>
               <ol id="d946e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e16">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                Is available to the Government without restriction from another source;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e21">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                Closely resembles a pending competitive acquisition requirement;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e26">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
								                Does not relate to the activity’s mission; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e31">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
								                Does not demonstrate an innovative and unique method, approach, or concept, or is otherwise not deemed a meritorious proposal.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e36">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            The contracting officer may commence negotiations on a sole source basis only when-</p>
               <ol id="d946e71" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e42">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                An unsolicited proposal has received a favorable comprehensive evaluation;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e47">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                A justification and approval has been obtained (see <xref href="6.302-1.dita#FAR_6_302_1"
                              base="i1119466"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">6.302-1</xref>(a)(2)(i) for research proposals or other appropriate provisions of <xref href="Subpart_6.3.dita#FAR_Subpart_6_3"
                              base="i1119434"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  6.3</xref>, and <xref href="6.303-2.dita#FAR_6_303_2"
                              base="i1119771"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">6.303-2</xref>(c));</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e61">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
								                The agency technical office sponsoring the contract furnishes the necessary funds; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d974e66">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
								                The contracting officer has complied with the synopsis requirements of <xref href="Subpart_5.2.dita#FAR_Subpart_5_2"
                              base="i1120661"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  5.2</xref>.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
